rComments: Amazing prof! He is a bit awkward but approachable and willing to help you if you need it. Very generous and straight forward exams if you know the course content.

I found his midterms to be really easy, but I found myself relying a little too much on background knowledge from high school. He tended to overcomplicate even the simplest of concepts, and I had to do a lot of work outside of class just to understand what should have been clearly taught
